results.name: Number of cycles in range [A014137(n-1)..A014138(n-1)] of permutation A125985/A125986.
comment: The number of orbits (equivalence classes) to which Vaille's automorphism partitions the set of A000108(n) Dyck paths of semilength n. Note the non-monotone drop from a(9) to a(10).
